# SereneDB compiles extensions into the server binary, so the upstream
# LOAD / INSTALL / UPDATE EXTENSIONS statements are not supported. They must
# surface a clear SereneDB error that points users at the SereneDB issue
# tracker -- never a duckdb.org link, a local extension path, or a network
# download attempt (see https://github.com/serenedb/serenedb/issues/768).


statement error
LOAD inet;
----
db error: ERROR: LOAD is not supported by SereneDB: extensions are compiled into the server binary and cannot be loaded at runtime.
If you need the "inet" extension, please open an issue at https://github.com/serenedb/serenedb/issues.


statement error
LOAD 'spatial';
----
db error: ERROR: LOAD is not supported by SereneDB: extensions are compiled into the server binary and cannot be loaded at runtime.
If you need the "spatial" extension, please open an issue at https://github.com/serenedb/serenedb/issues.


statement error
INSTALL inet;
----
db error: ERROR: INSTALL is not supported by SereneDB: extensions are compiled into the server binary and cannot be installed at runtime.
If you need the "inet" extension, please open an issue at https://github.com/serenedb/serenedb/issues.


statement error
FORCE INSTALL inet;
----
db error: ERROR: INSTALL is not supported by SereneDB: extensions are compiled into the server binary and cannot be installed at runtime.
If you need the "inet" extension, please open an issue at https://github.com/serenedb/serenedb/issues.


statement error
INSTALL httpfs FROM community;
----
db error: ERROR: INSTALL is not supported by SereneDB: extensions are compiled into the server binary and cannot be installed at runtime.
If you need the "httpfs" extension, please open an issue at https://github.com/serenedb/serenedb/issues.


statement error
UPDATE EXTENSIONS;
----
db error: ERROR: UPDATE EXTENSIONS is not supported by SereneDB: extensions are compiled into the server binary and cannot be updated at runtime.
If you are missing an extension, please open an issue at https://github.com/serenedb/serenedb/issues.
